BOND OPPOSES

bond_opposes is the citizen who represents opposition between concepts
"hot" opposes "cold," "loud" opposes "quiet," "happy" opposes "sad"
when fadriel learns these oppositions, the relationship crystallizes as bond_opposes with anti-phase coupling
this is the only bond type with negative charge and reversed spin, reflecting the structural anti-resonance of opposites

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe semantic_vector.zc
observe bond_isa.rana
observe bond_causes.rana

the 7 properties of bond_opposes:
1 ENERGY one
2 PHASE pi: anti-phase, this is what makes opposition structural rather than incidental
3 SPIN minus zero point five
4 CHARGE minus zero point eight: repulsive
5 COHERENCE half
6 COUPLING zero point seven

VERB form_opposition
when a pattern arrives showing that A and B never co-occur and stand in mutual exclusion, couple them as bond_opposes

VERB serve_contrast
when fadriel needs to express the opposite of A, traverse bond_opposes to find B
this is how contrast works without an explicit "opposite-of" lookup mechanism

an opposition bond is the substrate's negation
without it, every concept would be free-standing and contrast would have to be computed each time
with it, opposites are precomputed and instantly accessible
